==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stoppage
<hw>Stop"page</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of stopping,
or arresting progress, motion, or action; also, the state of being
stopped; <as>as, the <ex>stoppage</ex> of the circulation of the blood;
the <ex>stoppage</ex> of commerce.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stopped</ent>⟦br⟧
